#: templates/profile.html:5
msgid "Profile"
msgstr ""

#: templates/profile.html:18
msgid ""
"Born in 1994 in Gunma, Japan, I spent about six years in the IT industry, "
"advising enterprises on AI strategy and DevSecOps as a consultant focused on "
"AI and application security — helping organizations navigate digital "
"transformation."
msgstr ""

#: templates/profile.html:21
msgid ""
"I later earned a Dual Degree MBA-MSIS at Baylor University, broadening my "
"perspective across two continents and multiple industries."
msgstr ""

#: templates/profile.html:24
msgid ""
"After graduation, I will join Hitachi, Ltd. as an AI Strategy Staff, driving "
"the formulation and execution of enterprise-wide AI strategy."
msgstr ""

#: templates/profile.html:27
msgid ""
"Alongside my career, I teach English and social studies to junior high "
"school students at a local cram school — because I believe in unlocking "
"potential at every stage of life."
msgstr ""

